,["up","","Buzz","Everett Bogue","This is the first part of an interview I did with \u003cspan class\u003d\"proflinkWrapper\"\u003e\u003cspan class\u003d\"proflinkPrefix\"\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href\u003d\"https://plus.google.com/103387115750389541724\" class\u003d\"proflink\" oid\u003d\"103387115750389541724\"\u003ePraveen Puri\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e. \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eHighlights: \u0026quot;There’s no certain path to success in the online space. In Minimalist Business I talk about how to keep overhead low, experiment, measure, and untether from what isn’t working.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eThe only way to find out if my work is going to land in the online space is to push it out into the world and see how it lands.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eIf there was a surefire path to success, everyone would be doing it, and it wouldn’t be a path anymore – it’d be a really crowded highway.\u0026quot;",1332188461010,"https://web.archive.org/web/20120322202814/http://www.google.com/favicon.ico",[[,"Everett Bogue","Part II is here: \u003ca href\u003d\"http://simple-trading-system.blogspot.com/2012/03/interview-with-ev-bogue-author-of_20.html\" class\u003d\"ot-anchor\"\u003ehttp://simple-trading-system.blogspot.com/2012/03/interview-with-ev-bogue-author-of_20.html\u003c/a\u003e",1332271048683,"z12ldte4muqbd12oh04chb24yurjeftxxqw0k#1332271048683682",,"116298207273891385223","z12ldte4muqbd12oh04chb24yurjeftxxqw0k",0,1,"./116298207273891385223",1,,,0,[,,,,,,,,,,,,[]
