,["up","","Buzz","Everett Bogue","If you\u0026#39;re interested in photo editing – Adobe Photoshop CS6 is in free beta right now. --\u0026gt; \u003ca href\u003d\"http://labs.adobe.com/technologies/photoshopcs6/\" class\u003d\"ot-anchor\"\u003ehttp://labs.adobe.com/technologies/photoshopcs6/\u003c/a\u003e",1332400437962,"https://web.archive.org/web/20120322202814/http://www.google.com/favicon.ico",[]
