,["up","","Buzz","Everett Bogue","\u003cb\u003eMinimalist Business is relaunching on Tuesday March 13th\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eIt\u0026#39;s completely re-written, from scratch. Minimalist Business was a book I originally wrote two years ago about how I was living and working from anywhere in the world. Now, it\u0026#39;s a brand new book. Publishing is evolving, books have to evolve with it.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eThe new Minimalist Business is about creating zero overhead online businesses in order to live and work anywhere in the world. \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eThe reworked edition has been updated with all of the knowledge I\u0026#39;ve gained from doing business online over the past 3 years.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eThere\u0026#39;s going to be an early-bird price for 24 hours. If you\u0026#39;re interested in hearing more, head over to \u003ca href\u003d\"http://www.minimalistbusiness.com/\" class\u003d\"ot-anchor\"\u003ehttp://www.minimalistbusiness.com/\u003c/a\u003e and sign up for free updates in your inbox. I\u0026#39;ll get in touch with more details in your inbox.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eAlternatively, you can sign up for free inbox updates about Minimalist Business here: \u003ca href\u003d\"http://eepurl.com/jGHHv\" class\u003d\"ot-anchor\"\u003ehttp://eepurl.com/jGHHv\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eI\u0026#39;d like to ask if you\u0026#39;d be willing to hear more. If you don\u0026#39;t, just ignore this message. The 24 hour early-bird launch sale will continue without your knowledge.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eBest,\u003cbr /\u003e–Ev",1331525934955,"https://web.archive.org/web/20120322202814/http://www.google.com/favicon.ico",[]
,"z13fcd1g4vmsdjvt523dslbqpvumyjjhr04","","s:updates:esshare",[]
,[]
