});</script><div id="116298207273891385223-posts-page" class="k-Ya-Pn" role="tabpanel"><div class="kM5Oeb-RlcU0e"></div><div class="o8dQjb"><div class="kM5Oeb-zPJ5vc WkW9Rd"></div><div class="kM5Oeb-aLnjbc dbiwwb UFLnRe"><span class="Q88d9e"></span><div class="k-da-zf"></div></div><script>window.jstiming.load.tick('streamStart');</script><div guidedhelpid="streamcontent" class="Cw4PGf SG rnILlb"><h2 class="k-Bb">Stream</h2><div class="lzqA1d"><div id="update-z12gs10zrzuey3nzt04chb24yurjeftxxqw0k" tabindex="0" class="Wbhcze Te"><div class="CPLjOe Ye"><div class="Wl"><h3 class="k-Bb"><span class="qk">Everett Bogue</span></h3><span role="button" class="c-C Hf VV0qQb" title="Options menu" tabindex="0" aria-haspopup="true"></span><a href="./116298207273891385223" class="k-Qf-C-RySO6d oP" oid="116298207273891385223"><img src="//web.archive.org/web/20120322202814im_/https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-DTGZ0HgahRo/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAB48/rnwhNOjnFmE/s48-c-k/photo.jpg" width="48px" height="48px" alt="Everett Bogue's profile photo" class="Abw9Vd tg AI5FJe" oid="116298207273891385223"></a><div class="Ns"><span class="PJOqb"><a href="./116298207273891385223" class="cs2K7c qk is" oid="116298207273891385223">Everett Bogue</a></span><span class="SYTUvc Kg"> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span class="fD7nue qWSm4c"><a href="116298207273891385223/posts/ikf6whMZrE4" target="_blank" class="k-U-C k-Qf-C-RySO6d UzyZPb oj" style="display:none" title="Timestamp">Post date: 2012-03-22</a></span> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span role="button" class="c-C Lixzlc YQHDOd Nn ERIVId" title="Sharing details" tabindex="0" aria-haspopup="true">Public</span></span></div></div><div class="Vl EHlA9"><div class="WrStFb dXR9hf"><div class="rXnUBd">I was interviewed by <span class="proflinkWrapper"><span class="proflinkPrefix">+</span><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120322202814/https://plus.google.com/108240409864554105259" class="proflink" oid="108240409864554105259">Hugo Melo</a></span> about Minimalist Business marketing. <br/><br/>Excerpt from interview: &quot;The Internet is a vast place. There’s a potential to reach anyone in the world. However, I only want to hear about a product or service if it’s going to benefit me. This is true for everyone. Packaging information is not enough, it needs to be information which benefits other people.<br/><br/>The only option is to experiment with what we’re putting out into the world. If what I create today doesn’t land, I get an opportunity to try again tomorrow.<br/><br/>The goal of a Minimalist Business is flexibility. It’s about keeping overhead low so the business can change with a world in flux. It’s by growing, challenging, evolving myself that I’m able to grow my business.&quot;<br/><br/><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120322202814/http://hugomelo.com/minimalist-marketing/" class="ot-anchor">http://hugomelo.com/minimalist-marketing/</a></div></div><div class="Zbbru"><div class="s-r-fa FwSD8d"><img class="s-r-ql" src="//web.archive.org/web/20120322202814im_/https://s2.googleusercontent.com/s2/favicons?domain=hugomelo.com" alt=""><div class="s-r-za"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120322202814/http://hugomelo.com/minimalist-marketing/" class="ot-anchor s-r-za-C">How To Market a Minimalist Business</a></div><div class="s-r-Tb s-r-Ge-Pa" data-content-url="http://hugomelo.com/minimalist-marketing/" data-content-type="image/jpeg" style=""><img src="//web.archive.org/web/20120322202814im_/https://images1-focus-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/proxy?url=http://hugomelo.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/minimalistbusinessipad-300x3001.jpg&amp;container=focus&amp;gadget=a&amp;rewriteMime=image/*&amp;refresh=31536000&amp;resize_h=120&amp;no_expand=1" style="display:block;"></div><div class="s-r-Ge-ec">This week I got to sit down and interview Everett Bogue, a writer and entrepreneur that I really respect, who&#39;s recently rewritten his book Minimalist Business.</div><div class="s-r-vc"></div></div></div></div><div class="LwSBrb"></div><div class="LT1CSe vg" style="display:none;"><div class="Jdhf8e"></div></div><div class="sInvN Wk" style="display:none;"><div class="tvogXd yo" style="display:none"><span class="c-C D5h7zd nj "></span><div class="rg"><span role="button" class="c-C Hs" tabindex="0"></span></div></div><div class="UjdFAf Q32utd"><div class="epoPNd Js"><span role="button" class="c-C cgRpz Fs" style="display:none;" tabindex="0">0 older comments</span><div class="gemAid"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="update-z123slmrgzq3wz3gb04chb24yurjeftxxqw0k" tabindex="0" class="Wbhcze Te"><div class="CPLjOe Ye"><div class="Wl"><h3 class="k-Bb"><span class="qk">Everett Bogue</span></h3><span role="button" class="c-C Hf VV0qQb" title="Options menu" tabindex="0" aria-haspopup="true"></span><a href="./116298207273891385223" class="k-Qf-C-RySO6d oP" oid="116298207273891385223"><img src="//web.archive.org/web/20120322202814im_/https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-DTGZ0HgahRo/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAB48/rnwhNOjnFmE/s48-c-k/photo.jpg" width="48px" height="48px" alt="Everett Bogue's profile photo" class="Abw9Vd tg AI5FJe" oid="116298207273891385223"></a><div class="Ns"><span class="PJOqb"><a href="./116298207273891385223" class="cs2K7c qk is" oid="116298207273891385223">Everett Bogue</a></span><span class="SYTUvc Kg"> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span class="fD7nue qWSm4c"><a href="116298207273891385223/posts/PbhfrcqX7ZY" target="_blank" class="k-U-C k-Qf-C-RySO6d UzyZPb oj" style="display:none" title="Timestamp">Post date: 2012-03-22</a></span> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span role="button" class="c-C Lixzlc YQHDOd Nn ERIVId" title="Sharing details" tabindex="0" aria-haspopup="true">Public</span></span></div></div><div class="Vl EHlA9"><div class="WrStFb dXR9hf"><div class="rXnUBd">If you&#39;re interested in photo editing – Adobe Photoshop CS6 is in free beta right now. --&gt; <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120322202814/http://labs.adobe.com/technologies/photoshopcs6/" class="ot-anchor">http://labs.adobe.com/technologies/photoshopcs6/</a></div></div><div class="Zbbru"><div class="s-r-fa FwSD8d"><img class="s-r-ql" src="//web.archive.org/web/20120322202814im_/https://s2.googleusercontent.com/s2/favicons?domain=labs.adobe.com" alt=""><div class="s-r-za"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120322202814/http://labs.adobe.com/technologies/photoshopcs6/" class="ot-anchor s-r-za-C">Adobe Photoshop CS6 Beta | digital image editing software  - Adobe Labs</a></div><div class="s-r-Ge-ec">Explore Photoshop CS6 beta for a sneak preview and discover why Adobe Photoshop CS6 will be a whole new experience in digital image editing. Learn More.</div><div class="s-r-vc"></div></div></div></div><div class="LwSBrb Ao"><div class="Vt"><span role="button" class="c-C FdmHNd" tabindex="0">3 shares</span> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span class="lB8Ux"><span class="yQteKd">Jared CC, Matt Ragland, and Wafaa Dahmane</span></span></div></div><div class="LT1CSe vg" style="display:none;"><div class="Jdhf8e"></div></div><div class="sInvN Wk" style="display:none;"><div class="tvogXd yo" style="display:none"><span class="c-C D5h7zd nj "></span><div class="rg"><span role="button" class="c-C Hs" tabindex="0"></span></div></div><div class="UjdFAf Q32utd"><div class="epoPNd Js"><span role="button" class="c-C cgRpz Fs" style="display:none;" tabindex="0">0 older comments</span><div class="gemAid"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="update-z12ydz2qau3czr5dd23dslbqpvumyjjhr04" tabindex="0" class="Wbhcze Te"><div class="CPLjOe Ye"><div class="Wl"><h3 class="k-Bb"><span class="qk">Everett Bogue</span></h3><span role="button" class="c-C Hf VV0qQb" title="Options menu" tabindex="0" aria-haspopup="true"></span><a href="./116298207273891385223" class="k-Qf-C-RySO6d oP" oid="116298207273891385223"><img src="//web.archive.org/web/20120322202814im_/https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-DTGZ0HgahRo/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAB48/rnwhNOjnFmE/s48-c-k/photo.jpg" width="48px" height="48px" alt="Everett Bogue's profile photo" class="Abw9Vd tg AI5FJe" oid="116298207273891385223"></a><div class="Ns"><span class="PJOqb"><a href="./116298207273891385223" class="cs2K7c qk is" oid="116298207273891385223">Everett Bogue</a></span><span class="SYTUvc Kg"> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span class="fD7nue qWSm4c"><a href="116298207273891385223/posts/7tR92RS7gxB" target="_blank" class="k-U-C k-Qf-C-RySO6d UzyZPb oj" style="display:none" title="Timestamp">Post date: 2012-03-21</a></span> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span role="button" class="c-C Lixzlc YQHDOd Nn ERIVId" title="Sharing details" tabindex="0" aria-haspopup="true">Public</span></span></div></div><div class="Vl EHlA9"><div class="WrStFb dXR9hf"><div class="rXnUBd"><b>What is untethering?</b><br><br>Untethering is asking the question ‘why’ of everything in my life. If I can’t figure out a good reason for it exist, I cut the tether.<br><br>A tether is the tie that binds me to something I’m clinging to. I can be tethered to things, ideas, places, people, structures, cults, cultures, ways of being in the world, and more.<br><br>I almost always choose the tether, it often doesn’t choose me. I’m...</div><span role="button" class="c-C UqYPhc Ls" tabindex="0">Expand this post &raquo;</span></div><div class="Zbbru"></div></div><div class="LwSBrb Ao"><div class="Vt"><span role="button" class="c-C FdmHNd" tabindex="0">4 shares</span> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span class="lB8Ux"><span class="yQteKd">Chris French, Muhammed Yildirim, Peter Hinzmann, and Wafaa Dahmane</span></span></div></div><div class="LT1CSe vg" style="display:none;"><div class="Jdhf8e"></div></div><div class="sInvN Wk" style="display:none;"><div class="tvogXd yo" style="display:none"><span class="c-C D5h7zd nj "></span><div class="rg"><span role="button" class="c-C Hs" tabindex="0"></span></div></div><div class="UjdFAf Q32utd"><div class="epoPNd Js"><span role="button" class="c-C cgRpz Fs" style="display:none;" tabindex="0">0 older comments</span><div class="gemAid"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="update-z12ldte4muqbd12oh04chb24yurjeftxxqw0k" tabindex="0" class="Wbhcze Te"><div class="CPLjOe Ye"><div class="Wl"><h3 class="k-Bb"><span class="qk">Everett Bogue</span></h3><span role="button" class="c-C Hf VV0qQb" title="Options menu" tabindex="0" aria-haspopup="true"></span><a href="./116298207273891385223" class="k-Qf-C-RySO6d oP" oid="116298207273891385223"><img src="//web.archive.org/web/20120322202814im_/https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-DTGZ0HgahRo/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAB48/rnwhNOjnFmE/s48-c-k/photo.jpg" width="48px" height="48px" alt="Everett Bogue's profile photo" class="Abw9Vd tg AI5FJe" oid="116298207273891385223"></a><div class="Ns"><span class="PJOqb"><a href="./116298207273891385223" class="cs2K7c qk is" oid="116298207273891385223">Everett Bogue</a></span><span class="SYTUvc Kg"> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span class="fD7nue qWSm4c"><a href="116298207273891385223/posts/QbeMfvtDX6R" target="_blank" class="k-U-C k-Qf-C-RySO6d UzyZPb oj" style="display:none" title="Timestamp">Post date: 2012-03-19</a></span> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span role="button" class="c-C Lixzlc YQHDOd Nn ERIVId" title="Sharing details" tabindex="0" aria-haspopup="true">Public</span></span></div></div><div class="Vl EHlA9"><div class="WrStFb dXR9hf"><div class="rXnUBd">This is the first part of an interview I did with <span class="proflinkWrapper"><span class="proflinkPrefix">+</span><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120322202814/https://plus.google.com/103387115750389541724" class="proflink" oid="103387115750389541724">Praveen Puri</a></span>. <br/><br/>Highlights: &quot;There’s no certain path to success in the online space. In Minimalist Business I talk about how to keep overhead low, experiment, measure, and untether from what isn’t working.<br/><br/>The only way to find out if my work is going to land in the online space is to push it out into the world and see how it lands.<br/><br/>If there was a surefire path to success, everyone would be doing it, and it wouldn’t be a path anymore – it’d be a really crowded highway.&quot;</div></div><div class="Zbbru"><div class="s-r-fa FwSD8d"><img class="s-r-ql" src="//web.archive.org/web/20120322202814im_/https://s2.googleusercontent.com/s2/favicons?domain=simple-trading-system.blogspot.com" alt=""><div class="s-r-za"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120322202814/http://simple-trading-system.blogspot.com/2012/03/interview-with-ev-bogue-author-of.html" class="ot-anchor s-r-za-C">Stock Market Zen: Interview With Ev Bogue, Author of &quot;Minimalist Business&quot;, Part I</a></div><div class="s-r-Ge-ec">I recently conducted an interview with Ev Bogue, who has just released a completely rewritten version of his best-selling ebook &quot;Minimalist Business&quot;. Since Ev kindly took the time to provid...</div><div class="s-r-vc"></div></div></div></div><div class="LwSBrb"></div><div class="LT1CSe vg" style="display:none;"><div class="Jdhf8e"></div></div><div class="sInvN Wk"><div class="tvogXd yo" style="display:none"><span class="c-C D5h7zd nj "></span><div class="rg"><span role="button" class="c-C Hs" tabindex="0"><span class="aISsjb Cs">1</span><span class="Ds"> comment</span></span><span class="ys"> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span class="lB8Ux"><span class="yQteKd">Everett Bogue</span></span></span></div></div><div class="UjdFAf Q32utd"><div class="epoPNd Js"><span role="button" class="c-C cgRpz Fs" style="display:none;" tabindex="0">0 older comments</span><div class="gemAid"><div id="z12ldte4muqbd12oh04chb24yurjeftxxqw0k#1332271048683682" tabindex="0" class="wd bi2Sed"><div class="We"><a href="./116298207273891385223" class="k-Qf-C-RySO6d oP" oid="116298207273891385223"><img src="//web.archive.org/web/20120322202814im_/https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-DTGZ0HgahRo/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAB48/rnwhNOjnFmE/s32-c-k/photo.jpg" width="32px" height="32px" alt="Everett Bogue's profile photo" class="Abw9Vd tg st hf" oid="116298207273891385223"></a><div><a href="./116298207273891385223" class="cs2K7c qk xs" rel="nofollow" oid="116298207273891385223">Everett Bogue</a> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span class="kH">Part II is here: <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120322202814/http://simple-trading-system.blogspot.com/2012/03/interview-with-ev-bogue-author-of_20.html" class="ot-anchor">http://simple-trading-system.blogspot.com/2012/03/interview-with-ev-bogue-author-of_20.html</a></span></div><div class="I2"><span class="WKExab"></span> &nbsp;&nbsp; <span class="Yg14nf zo"><div class="Jdhf8e zidWKb Ir c-wa-Da"></div></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="update-z13bybgrkyrsyn34w04chb24yurjeftxxqw0k" tabindex="0" class="Wbhcze Te"><div class="CPLjOe Ye"><div class="Wl"><h3 class="k-Bb"><span class="qk">Everett Bogue</span></h3><span role="button" class="c-C Hf VV0qQb" title="Options menu" tabindex="0" aria-haspopup="true"></span><a href="./116298207273891385223" class="k-Qf-C-RySO6d oP" oid="116298207273891385223"><img src="//web.archive.org/web/20120322202814im_/https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-DTGZ0HgahRo/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAB48/rnwhNOjnFmE/s48-c-k/photo.jpg" width="48px" height="48px" alt="Everett Bogue's profile photo" class="Abw9Vd tg AI5FJe" oid="116298207273891385223"></a><div class="Ns"><span class="PJOqb"><a href="./116298207273891385223" class="cs2K7c qk is" oid="116298207273891385223">Everett Bogue</a></span><span class="SYTUvc Kg"> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span class="fD7nue qWSm4c"><a href="116298207273891385223/posts/T7NKdCtyhwc" target="_blank" class="k-U-C k-Qf-C-RySO6d UzyZPb oj" style="display:none" title="Timestamp">Post date: 2012-03-19</a></span> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span role="button" class="c-C Lixzlc YQHDOd Nn ERIVId" title="Sharing details" tabindex="0" aria-haspopup="true">Public</span></span></div></div><div class="Vl EHlA9"><div class="WrStFb dXR9hf"><div class="rXnUBd"><b>The future of the evolving book</b><br><br>For the last six months I’ve lived in flexible housing situations – Airbnb, hotels in Mexico, etc. I do this was because I want greater autonomy in my life. I could be tied down with a 6-month or 1-year lease. But do I want to?<br><br>Living in a flexible living situation gives me greater freedom. If I want to leave at the end of the month, I can.<br><br>When I reworked <i>Minimalist Business...</i></div><span role="button" class="c-C UqYPhc Ls" tabindex="0">Expand this post &raquo;</span></div><div class="Zbbru"></div></div><div class="LwSBrb"></div><div class="LT1CSe vg" style="display:none;"><div class="Jdhf8e"></div></div><div class="sInvN Wk" style="display:none;"><div class="tvogXd yo" style="display:none"><span class="c-C D5h7zd nj "></span><div class="rg"><span role="button" class="c-C Hs" tabindex="0"></span></div></div><div class="UjdFAf Q32utd"><div class="epoPNd Js"><span role="button" class="c-C cgRpz Fs" style="display:none;" tabindex="0">0 older comments</span><div class="gemAid"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="update-z12gvzxrwka0ynp3b23dslbqpvumyjjhr04" tabindex="0" class="Wbhcze Te"><div class="CPLjOe Ye"><div class="Wl"><h3 class="k-Bb"><span class="qk">Everett Bogue</span></h3><span role="button" class="c-C Hf VV0qQb" title="Options menu" tabindex="0" aria-haspopup="true"></span><a href="./116298207273891385223" class="k-Qf-C-RySO6d oP" oid="116298207273891385223"><img src="//web.archive.org/web/20120322202814im_/https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-DTGZ0HgahRo/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAB48/rnwhNOjnFmE/s48-c-k/photo.jpg" width="48px" height="48px" alt="Everett Bogue's profile photo" class="Abw9Vd tg AI5FJe" oid="116298207273891385223"></a><div class="Ns"><span class="PJOqb"><a href="./116298207273891385223" class="cs2K7c qk is" oid="116298207273891385223">Everett Bogue</a></span><span class="SYTUvc Kg"> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span class="fD7nue qWSm4c"><a href="116298207273891385223/posts/JLf9Kr5FNh6" target="_blank" class="k-U-C k-Qf-C-RySO6d UzyZPb oj" style="display:none" title="Timestamp">Post date: 2012-03-18</a></span> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span role="button" class="c-C Lixzlc YQHDOd Nn ERIVId" title="Sharing details" tabindex="0" aria-haspopup="true">Public</span></span></div></div><div class="Vl EHlA9"><div class="WrStFb dXR9hf"><div class="rXnUBd">What information do you want to know about a person when you first discover their online presence?</div></div><div class="Zbbru"></div></div><div class="LwSBrb"></div><div class="LT1CSe vg" style="display:none;"><div class="Jdhf8e"></div></div><div class="sInvN Wk"><div class="tvogXd yo"><span class="c-C D5h7zd nj "></span><div class="rg"><span role="button" class="c-C Hs" tabindex="0"><span class="aISsjb Cs">13</span><span class="Ds"> comments</span></span><span class="ys"> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span class="lB8Ux"><span class="yQteKd">Wafaa Dahmane, Beat Schindler, Kahnrad Awalt, Steven Williams, Ross Hill and 1 more</span></span></span></div></div><div class="UjdFAf Q32utd"><div class="epoPNd Js"><span role="button" class="c-C cgRpz Fs" style="display:none;" tabindex="0">0 older comments</span><div class="gemAid"><div id="z12gvzxrwka0ynp3b23dslbqpvumyjjhr04#1332422463458853" tabindex="0" class="wd bi2Sed"><div class="We"><a href="./109460563674970842836" class="k-Qf-C-RySO6d oP" oid="109460563674970842836"><img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20120322202814im_/https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-mfrccoR7wAA/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAAAA/jknnuWdJw0E/s32-c-k/photo.jpg" width="32px" height="32px" alt="Wafaa Dahmane's profile photo" class="Abw9Vd tg st hf" oid="109460563674970842836"></a><div><a href="./109460563674970842836" class="cs2K7c qk xs" rel="nofollow" oid="109460563674970842836">Wafaa Dahmane</a> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span class="kH">what they do, their interests, their thoughts ....</span></div><div class="I2"><span class="WKExab"></span> &nbsp;&nbsp; <span class="Yg14nf zo"><div class="Jdhf8e zidWKb Ir c-wa-Da"></div></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="update-z13gvzrbowqfsjz1n23dslbqpvumyjjhr04" tabindex="0" class="Wbhcze Te"><div class="CPLjOe Ye"><div class="Wl"><h3 class="k-Bb"><span class="qk">Everett Bogue</span></h3><span role="button" class="c-C Hf VV0qQb" title="Options menu" tabindex="0" aria-haspopup="true"></span><a href="./116298207273891385223" class="k-Qf-C-RySO6d oP" oid="116298207273891385223"><img src="//web.archive.org/web/20120322202814im_/https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-DTGZ0HgahRo/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAB48/rnwhNOjnFmE/s48-c-k/photo.jpg" width="48px" height="48px" alt="Everett Bogue's profile photo" class="Abw9Vd tg AI5FJe" oid="116298207273891385223"></a><div class="Ns"><span class="PJOqb"><a href="./116298207273891385223" class="cs2K7c qk is" oid="116298207273891385223">Everett Bogue</a></span><span class="SYTUvc Kg"> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span class="fD7nue qWSm4c"><a href="116298207273891385223/posts/9hAeCCKSND6" target="_blank" class="k-U-C k-Qf-C-RySO6d UzyZPb oj" style="display:none" title="Timestamp">Post date: 2012-03-13</a></span> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span role="button" class="c-C Lixzlc YQHDOd Nn ERIVId" title="Sharing details" tabindex="0" aria-haspopup="true">Public</span></span></div></div><div class="Vl EHlA9"><div class="WrStFb dXR9hf"><div class="rXnUBd">I launched an evolving digital book on the day the physical encyclopedia died. Coincidence (or fate?!)</div></div><div class="Zbbru"></div></div><div class="LwSBrb"></div><div class="LT1CSe vg" style="display:none;"><div class="Jdhf8e"></div></div><div class="sInvN Wk"><div class="tvogXd yo"><span class="c-C D5h7zd nj "></span><div class="rg"><span role="button" class="c-C Hs" tabindex="0"><span class="aISsjb Cs">13</span><span class="Ds"> comments</span></span><span class="ys"> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span class="lB8Ux"><span class="yQteKd">Conni Biesalski, Chris Oakley, Michael Xander, Jeferson Brito, and Kahnrad Awalt</span></span></span></div></div><div class="UjdFAf Q32utd"><div class="epoPNd Js"><span role="button" class="c-C cgRpz Fs" style="display:none;" tabindex="0">0 older comments</span><div class="gemAid"><div id="z13gvzrbowqfsjz1n23dslbqpvumyjjhr04#1331823679112382" tabindex="0" class="wd bi2Sed"><div class="We"><a href="./102590617779936302022" class="k-Qf-C-RySO6d oP" oid="102590617779936302022"><img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20120322202814im_/https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-04rO6X0Msoo/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAAAA/dE3wDZm-c_A/s32-c-k/photo.jpg" width="32px" height="32px" alt="Conni Biesalski's profile photo" class="Abw9Vd tg st hf" oid="102590617779936302022"></a><div><a href="./102590617779936302022" class="cs2K7c qk xs" rel="nofollow" oid="102590617779936302022">Conni Biesalski</a> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span class="kH">Fate! Loving the book, Ev. Hope to get together for an interview soon?</span></div><div class="I2"><span class="WKExab"></span> &nbsp;&nbsp; <span class="Yg14nf zo"><div class="Jdhf8e zidWKb Ir c-wa-Da"></div></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="update-z13sexl4vxjkulz0523dslbqpvumyjjhr04" tabindex="0" class="Wbhcze Te"><div class="CPLjOe Ye"><div class="Wl"><h3 class="k-Bb"><span class="qk">Everett Bogue</span></h3><span role="button" class="c-C Hf VV0qQb" title="Options menu" tabindex="0" aria-haspopup="true"></span><a href="./116298207273891385223" class="k-Qf-C-RySO6d oP" oid="116298207273891385223"><img src="//web.archive.org/web/20120322202814im_/https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-DTGZ0HgahRo/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAB48/rnwhNOjnFmE/s48-c-k/photo.jpg" width="48px" height="48px" alt="Everett Bogue's profile photo" class="Abw9Vd tg AI5FJe" oid="116298207273891385223"></a><div class="Ns"><span class="PJOqb"><a href="./116298207273891385223" class="cs2K7c qk is" oid="116298207273891385223">Everett Bogue</a></span><span class="SYTUvc Kg"> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span class="fD7nue qWSm4c"><a href="116298207273891385223/posts/1zvrSMbSt5M" target="_blank" class="k-U-C k-Qf-C-RySO6d UzyZPb oj" style="display:none" title="Timestamp">Post date: 2012-03-13</a></span> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span role="button" class="c-C Lixzlc YQHDOd Nn ERIVId" title="Sharing details" tabindex="0" aria-haspopup="true">Public</span></span></div></div><div class="Vl EHlA9"><div class="WrStFb dXR9hf"><div class="rXnUBd">I&#39;m feeling proud and excited to announce the reworked edition of Minimalist Business has launched.<br/><br/><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120322202814/http://buy.minimalistbusiness.com/" class="ot-anchor">http://buy.minimalistbusiness.com/</a></div></div><div class="Zbbru"><div class="s-r-fa FwSD8d"><img class="s-r-ql" src="//web.archive.org/web/20120322202814im_/https://s2.googleusercontent.com/s2/favicons?domain=buy.minimalistbusiness.com" alt=""><div class="s-r-za"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120322202814/http://buy.minimalistbusiness.com/" class="ot-anchor s-r-za-C">Minimalist Business | How to Live and Work Anywhere</a></div><div class="s-r-Tb s-r-Ge-Pa" data-content-url="http://buy.minimalistbusiness.com/" data-content-type="image/jpeg" style=""><img src="//web.archive.org/web/20120322202814im_/https://images1-focus-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/proxy?url=http://buy.minimalistbusiness.com/minimalistbusiness.jpg&amp;container=focus&amp;gadget=a&amp;rewriteMime=image/*&amp;refresh=31536000&amp;resize_h=120&amp;no_expand=1" style="display:block;"></div><div class="s-r-Ge-ec">How to live and work anywhere. For the last three years, I&#39;ve been running an experiment. Can I live and work from anywhere in the world? The answer, for me at least, seems to be &#39;yes, I can l...</div><div class="s-r-vc"></div></div></div></div><div class="LwSBrb Ao"><div class="Vt"><span role="button" class="c-C FdmHNd" tabindex="0">5 shares</span> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span class="lB8Ux"><span class="yQteKd">Barry Morris, Charlie Forness, Conni Biesalski, Linda Gabriel, and caleb rogers</span></span></div></div><div class="LT1CSe vg" style="display:none;"><div class="Jdhf8e"></div></div><div class="sInvN Wk" style="display:none;"><div class="tvogXd yo" style="display:none"><span class="c-C D5h7zd nj "></span><div class="rg"><span role="button" class="c-C Hs" tabindex="0"></span></div></div><div class="UjdFAf Q32utd"><div class="epoPNd Js"><span role="button" class="c-C cgRpz Fs" style="display:none;" tabindex="0">0 older comments</span><div class="gemAid"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="update-z13fcd1g4vmsdjvt523dslbqpvumyjjhr04" tabindex="0" class="Wbhcze Te"><div class="CPLjOe Ye"><div class="Wl"><h3 class="k-Bb"><span class="qk">Everett Bogue</span></h3><span role="button" class="c-C Hf VV0qQb" title="Options menu" tabindex="0" aria-haspopup="true"></span><a href="./116298207273891385223" class="k-Qf-C-RySO6d oP" oid="116298207273891385223"><img src="//web.archive.org/web/20120322202814im_/https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-DTGZ0HgahRo/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAB48/rnwhNOjnFmE/s48-c-k/photo.jpg" width="48px" height="48px" alt="Everett Bogue's profile photo" class="Abw9Vd tg AI5FJe" oid="116298207273891385223"></a><div class="Ns"><span class="PJOqb"><a href="./116298207273891385223" class="cs2K7c qk is" oid="116298207273891385223">Everett Bogue</a></span><span class="SYTUvc Kg"> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span class="fD7nue qWSm4c"><a href="116298207273891385223/posts/7LNdmEBx8Jh" target="_blank" class="k-U-C k-Qf-C-RySO6d UzyZPb oj" style="display:none" title="Timestamp">Post date: 2012-03-11</a></span> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span role="button" class="c-C Lixzlc YQHDOd Nn ERIVId" title="Sharing details" tabindex="0" aria-haspopup="true">Public</span></span></div></div><div class="Vl EHlA9"><div class="WrStFb dXR9hf"><div class="rXnUBd"><b>Minimalist Business is relaunching on Tuesday March 13th</b><br><br>It&#39;s completely re-written, from scratch. Minimalist Business was a book I originally wrote two years ago about how I was living and working from anywhere in the world. Now, it&#39;s a brand new book. Publishing is evolving, books have to evolve with it.<br><br>The new Minimalist Business is about creating zero overhead online businesses in order to live ...</div><span role="button" class="c-C UqYPhc Ls" tabindex="0">Expand this post &raquo;</span></div><div class="Zbbru"></div></div><div class="LwSBrb Ao"><div class="Vt"><span role="button" class="c-C FdmHNd" tabindex="0">1 share</span> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span class="lB8Ux"><span class="yQteKd">Giovani Saintiny</span></span></div></div><div class="LT1CSe vg" style="display:none;"><div class="Jdhf8e"></div></div><div class="sInvN Wk" style="display:none;"><div class="tvogXd yo" style="display:none"><span class="c-C D5h7zd nj "></span><div class="rg"><span role="button" class="c-C Hs" tabindex="0"></span></div></div><div class="UjdFAf Q32utd"><div class="epoPNd Js"><span role="button" class="c-C cgRpz Fs" style="display:none;" tabindex="0">0 older comments</span><div class="gemAid"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="update-z134glmgppycy3uhg04chb24yurjeftxxqw0k" tabindex="0" class="Wbhcze Te"><div class="CPLjOe Ye"><div class="Wl"><h3 class="k-Bb"><span class="qk">Everett Bogue</span></h3><span role="button" class="c-C Hf VV0qQb" title="Options menu" tabindex="0" aria-haspopup="true"></span><a href="./116298207273891385223" class="k-Qf-C-RySO6d oP" oid="116298207273891385223"><img src="//web.archive.org/web/20120322202814im_/https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-DTGZ0HgahRo/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAB48/rnwhNOjnFmE/s48-c-k/photo.jpg" width="48px" height="48px" alt="Everett Bogue's profile photo" class="Abw9Vd tg AI5FJe" oid="116298207273891385223"></a><div class="Ns"><span class="PJOqb"><a href="./116298207273891385223" class="cs2K7c qk is" oid="116298207273891385223">Everett Bogue</a></span><span class="SYTUvc Kg"> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span class="fD7nue qWSm4c"><a href="116298207273891385223/posts/VudbndEYMJw" target="_blank" class="k-U-C k-Qf-C-RySO6d UzyZPb oj" style="display:none" title="Timestamp">Post date: 2012-03-11</a></span> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span role="button" class="c-C Lixzlc YQHDOd Nn ERIVId" title="Sharing details" tabindex="0" aria-haspopup="true">Public</span></span></div></div><div class="Vl EHlA9"><div class="WrStFb dXR9hf"><div class="rXnUBd">I&#39;m curious. What percentage do you consider yourself...?<br/><br/>1. Artist<br/>2. Craftsman<br/>3. Salesman</div></div><div class="Zbbru"></div></div><div class="LwSBrb"></div><div class="LT1CSe vg" style="display:none;"><div class="Jdhf8e"></div></div><div class="sInvN Wk"><div class="tvogXd yo"><span class="c-C D5h7zd nj "></span><div class="rg"><span role="button" class="c-C Hs" tabindex="0"><span class="aISsjb Cs">15</span><span class="Ds"> comments</span></span><span class="ys"> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span class="lB8Ux"><span class="yQteKd">Kristoffer Nilsson, George Bowles, Jacinda Davis, Lincoln Hammond, Kahnrad Awalt and 1 more</span></span></span></div></div><div class="UjdFAf Q32utd"><div class="epoPNd Js"><span role="button" class="c-C cgRpz Fs" style="display:none;" tabindex="0">0 older comments</span><div class="gemAid"><div id="z134glmgppycy3uhg04chb24yurjeftxxqw0k#1331975082943677" tabindex="0" class="wd bi2Sed"><div class="We"><a href="./112197301662829038332" class="k-Qf-C-RySO6d oP" oid="112197301662829038332"><img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20120322202814im_/https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-6S4wEC03t4w/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAAAA/0__J2WEXbbg/s32-c-k/photo.jpg" width="32px" height="32px" alt="Kristoffer Nilsson's profile photo" class="Abw9Vd tg st hf" oid="112197301662829038332"></a><div><a href="./112197301662829038332" class="cs2K7c qk xs" rel="nofollow" oid="112197301662829038332">Kristoffer Nilsson</a> &nbsp;-&nbsp; <span class="kH">salesman</span></div><div class="I2"><span class="WKExab"></span> &nbsp;&nbsp; <span class="Yg14nf zo"><div class="Jdhf8e zidWKb Ir c-wa-Da"></div></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="gH"><div class="CfrSGe WY2Dce" style="display: none"><span role="button" class="c-C E4V1D fFgAkc" title="Load more posts" tabindex="0">More</span><span class="GUgnx xkC83c" style="display: none"><span class="yG12ye">Loading...</span></span></div></div><div class="a7p1xb" style="display:none"></div></div><script>window.jstiming.load.tick('streamEnd');</script></div></div><div id="116298207273891385223-about-page" class="k-Ya-Pn k-Ya-Bb" role="tabpanel"><div class="KzjeM"><div class="sNcs4c"><div class="kM5Oeb-uoq5sb Sd8iK KtnyId IzbGp"><h2 class="Wfskpc c-wa-Da">Introduction</h2><div class="aYm0te c-wa-Da note"><p>Hi, I’m Everett Bogue.</p>
<p>In 2009, I quit my job and started throwing out my stuff. I’ve been living out of a backpack since. I create location independent Minimalist Businesses. I’m the author of <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120322202814/http://www.minimalistbusiness.com/" target="_blank">Minimalist Business</a>. I live and work from anywhere in the world.</p>
<p>I’m interested in how we communicate with humans and machines on the modern web. Technology is evolving at an exponential rate –we’re evolving with it.</p>
<p>I’m interested in doing things that scare me. I grow and find purpose when I’m living in an uncertain world. When everyone is usually heading away from challenging things, I tend to head towards them.</p>
<p>I’ve authored a digital products over the last 3 years, including The Art of Being Minimalist, Minimalist Business, Augmented Humanity, Taking Your Book to the Web, Evolving Your Digital Work and a half dozen others. My current digital product is <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120322202814/http://www.minimalistbusiness.com/" target="_blank">Minimalist Business</a>.</p>
<p>I’m interested in how we gather permission to contact other humans in the world. Like an Airport or a busy market in India, the Internet is a crowded place. I’d like to ask permission before I offer things to you.</p>
<p>Would you be willing to <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120322202814/http://www.evbogue.com/" target="_blank">hear more from me</a>?<br></p></div></div><div class="kM5Oeb-d8pDRe KtnyId IzbGp"><h2 class="Wfskpc c-wa-Da">Bragging rights</h2><div class="aYm0te c-wa-Da note">Kindergarten dropout</div></div><div class="KtnyId kM5Oeb-ltU7Zc IzbGp"><h2 class="Wfskpc c-wa-Da">Employment</h2><div class="aYm0te c-wa-Da"><ul class="FLMe8d"><li class="TPAeZc"><div class="j1SW4 org">Author of Minimalist Business. I will teach you to create a zero-overhead business to live and work from anywhere in the world.</div><div class="SvqDDb">CEO of Minimalist Business, 2009 - present</div></li></ul></div></div><div class="KtnyId kM5Oeb-iTT2dc IzbGp"><h2 class="Wfskpc c-wa-Da">Education</h2><div class="aYm0te c-wa-Da"><ul class="FLMe8d"><li class="TPAeZc"><div class="j1SW4">New York University</div><div class="SvqDDb">Journalism + Dance, 2003 - 2006</div></li></ul></div></div><div class="KtnyId kM5Oeb-Ymm9ke IzbGp"><h2 class="Wfskpc c-wa-Da">Places lived</h2><div class="aYm0te lh1VRe c-wa-Da"><img class="pYGNmf c-wa-Da" alt="Map of the places this user has lived" id="oz-profile-location-map" src="//web.archive.org/web/20120322202814im_/https://maps-api-ssl.google.com/maps/api/staticmap?size=195x150&amp;sensor=false&amp;client=google-profiles&amp;language=en&amp;markers=size:small%7Ccolor:blue%7C37.77493,-122.419416&amp;markers=size:small%7Ccolor:green%7C20.622018,-105.228457%7C47.60621,-122.332071%7C40.014986,-105.270546%7C41.878114,-87.629798%7C40.714353,-74.005973%7C45.523452,-122.676207%7C41.878114,-87.629798%7C21.033333,105.85&amp;signature=yaHOgmFt13WAXxvfdF6xm9yYJjY%3D"/><ul class="WdkQGe c-wa-Da"><li class="p34YJb KnK5Cc" title="San Francisco, CA"><div class="adr">San Francisco, CA</div></li><li class="p34YJb" title="Puerto Vallarta, MX">Puerto Vallarta, MX</li><li class="p34YJb" title="Seattle, WA">Seattle, WA</li><li class="p34YJb" title="Boulder, CO">Boulder, CO</li><li class="p34YJb" title="Chicago, IL">Chicago, IL</li><li class="p34YJb" title="New York, NY">New York, NY</li><li class="p34YJb" title="Portland, OR">Portland, OR</li><li class="p34YJb" title="Chicago, IL">Chicago, IL</li><li class="p34YJb" title="Hanoi, Vietnam">Hanoi, Vietnam</li></ul></div></div><div class="kM5Oeb-SxIGbc KtnyId AfLLHd IzbGp NlK5sd"><h2 class="Wfskpc c-wa-Da">Home</h2><div class="aYm0te mbwpyc c-wa-Da">How can people reach you at home?</div></div><div class="kM5Oeb-bO0iUc KtnyId AfLLHd IzbGp NlK5sd"><h2 class="Wfskpc c-wa-Da">Work</h2><div class="aYm0te mbwpyc c-wa-Da">How can people reach you at work?</div></div><div class="kM5Oeb-fYiPJe KtnyId IzbGp"><h2 class="Wfskpc c-wa-Da">Gender</h2><div class="aYm0te c-wa-Da">Male</div></div><div class="kM5Oeb-fPo65b KtnyId IzbGp"><h2 class="Wfskpc c-wa-Da">Other names</h2><div class="aYm0te c-wa-Da">Everett Bogue</div></div></div><div class="bgj5b"><div class="kM5Oeb-OP8lce IzbGp KtnyId GpTjlb Sd8iK hnuPlc"><span><div class="c-wa-Da"><h2 class="CuJEEf">Contributor to</h2></div><div class="c-wa-Da"></div></span><ul class="FLMe8d PLDbbf"><li><img alt="" class="QHBEn" src="//web.archive.org/web/20120322202814im_/https://s2.googleusercontent.com/s2/favicons?alt=p&amp;domain=www.evbogue.com"/><div class="dcQzjb C"><a class="Qc0zVe url" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120322202814/http://www.evbogue.com/" rel="contributor-to" target="_blank" title="Evbogue.com">Evbogue.com</a></div></li><li><img alt="" class="QHBEn" src="//web.archive.org/web/20120322202814im_/https://s2.googleusercontent.com/s2/favicons?alt=p&amp;domain=www.minimalistbusiness.com"/><div class="dcQzjb C"><a class="Qc0zVe url" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120322202814/http://www.minimalistbusiness.com/" rel="contributor-to" target="_blank" title="Minimalist Business">Minimalist Business</a></div></li></ul></div></div><div style="clear: both"></div></div><div class="kM5Oeb-npMLoc"></div><script>window.jstiming.load.tick('aboutEnd');</s